# Internal tenancy details — never commit real values, use <PLACEHOLDER> tokens
# Documented in .planning/SECURITY.md and ~/.claude/CLAUDE.md "OCI Tenancy Boundaries".
# These paths are common destinations for files that accidentally collect OCIDs/IPs/datakeys:
.planning/STATUS-*.md
.planning/tmp/
.planning/intel/
.planning/graphs/
graphify-out/
deploy/oke/bootstrap-emdemo-secrets.sh
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfvars
!*.tfvars.example
outputs.json
**/outputs.json
**/instance-ips-output.json
**/jumphost.json
**/.ocir-token
**/auth-token.txt
**/oci_api_key_*.pem

# Logs + test output
*.log
.playwright-cli/
playwright-report/
test-results/
